<body style="background-color:#FFE3FE;">
<h1 class="text-info mt-4 text-center" style="border:2px solid Violet;"> ✨🧚🏻🌛 Your Crush Profile 🌜🧚🏼‍♂️✨ </h1>
<main>
<hr>
<p><strong> Name: </strong><%= @crush.name %></p><hr>
<p><strong> DOB: </strong><%= @crush.dob%></p><hr>
<p><strong> Your Crush's Sign: </strong><%= @crush.sign %></p><hr>
<p><strong> Symbol: </strong><%= image_tag @info["data"]["result"]["partner"]["Image"] %></p><hr>
<p><strong> Element: </strong><%= @crush.element %></p><hr>
<p><strong> Quality: </strong><%= @crush.quality %></p><hr>
<p><strong> Compatibility: </strong><%= @crush.compatibility %></p><hr>
<p><strong> Compatibility Details: </strong><%= @crush.details %></p><hr>
<p><strong> Postive Traits of this Crush: </strong><%= @crush.positive %></p><hr>
<p><strong> Negative Traits of this Crush: </strong><%= @crush.negative %></p><hr>


<%= link_to "Add to Crushlist", new_user_crush_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %> ✨
<%= link_to "See your Crush list", user_crushes_path, class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %> ✨
<%= link_to "💁🏻‍♀️✨Friendzone this Crush ✨💁🏻‍♀️", friend_path(id: @crush.id), method: :patch, class: "btn btn-outline-primary" %><br>
<%= flash[:message] %><br>

</main>